CREATE VIEW emp_attendance AS SELECT empDays.EMPCODE empCode , EMPDAYS.DD dayDate, (CASE WHEN ta.DATE_ IS NOT NULL THEN ta.DATE_ WHEN req.from_date IS NOT NULL THEN req.FROM_DATE END) AS attendance_date, (CASE WHEN ta.DATE_ IS NOT NULL THEN ta.TIME_ WHEN req.from_date IS NOT NULL THEN req.PERIOD_FROM END) AS attendance_time, (CASE WHEN ta.DATE_ IS NOT NULL THEN (CASE WHEN ta.TRANS_TYPE='I' THEN 'IN' ELSE 'OUT' END ) WHEN req.FROM_DATE IS NOT NULL THEN (CASE WHEN req.REQUEST_TYPE=10 THEN 'IN' WHEN req.REQUEST_TYPE=11 THEN 'OUT' END ) END ) AS ATTENDANCE_Type, --(CASE WHEN ta.DATE_ IS NOT NULL THEN 'Fingerprint' WHEN req.from_date IS NOT NULL THEN 'Web' END) AS attendance_source, (CASE WHEN req.APPROVED =1 THEN 'Approved' WHEN req.APPROVED =99 THEN 'Rejected' WHEN ta.date_ IS NOT NULL THEN 'DontNeedApproval' WHEN (req.FROM_DATE IS NULL AND ta.DATE_ IS null) THEN 'DontNeedApproval' ELSE 'Incomplete' END) AS approval, (CASE WHEN req.INPUTTYPE=0 THEN 'Web_Attendance' WHEN req.INPUTTYPE=1 THEN 'Request_Attendance' WHEN req.INPUTTYPE=2 THEN 'Android_Attendance' WHEN ta.date_ IS NOT NULL THEN 'Fingerprint_Attendance' ELSE 'Absent' END) AS input_type, req.LONGITUDE AS longitude, req.LATITUDE latitude FROM ALL_EMP_DAYS empDays LEFT join TIME_ATTEND ta ON ta.EMP_CODE=empDays.EMPCODE AND ta.DATE_=EMPDAYS.DD LEFT join LOGIN_USERS_REQUESTS req ON req.EMPCODE=empDays.EMPCODE AND ((req.REQUEST_TYPE=10 OR req.REQUEST_TYPE=11) and TO_DATE(req.FROM_DATE,'DD-MM-YYYY')=TO_DATE(EMPDAYS.DD,'DD-MM-YYYY')) JOIN COMMON_EMPLOYEE emp ON emp.EMPCODE = empDays.EMPCODE ORDER BY empdays.DD,ta.time_,req.PERIOD_FROM asc;
DROP VIEW emp_attendance;

CREATE VIEW emp_attendance AS SELECT empDays.EMPCODE empCode , EMPDAYS.DD dayDate, (CASE WHEN ta.DATE_ IS NOT NULL THEN ta.DATE_ WHEN req.from_date IS NOT NULL THEN req.FROM_DATE END) AS attendance_date, (CASE WHEN ta.DATE_ IS NOT NULL THEN ta.TIME_ WHEN req.from_date IS NOT NULL THEN req.PERIOD_FROM END) AS attendance_time, (CASE WHEN ta.DATE_ IS NOT NULL THEN (CASE WHEN ta.TRANS_TYPE='I' THEN 'IN' ELSE 'OUT' END ) WHEN req.FROM_DATE IS NOT NULL THEN (CASE WHEN req.REQUEST_TYPE=10 THEN 'IN' WHEN req.REQUEST_TYPE=11 THEN 'OUT' END ) END ) AS ATTENDANCE_Type, --(CASE WHEN ta.DATE_ IS NOT NULL THEN 'Fingerprint' WHEN req.from_date IS NOT NULL THEN 'Web' END) AS attendance_source, (CASE WHEN req.APPROVED =1 THEN 'Approved' WHEN req.APPROVED =99 THEN 'Rejected' WHEN ta.date_ IS NOT NULL THEN 'DontNeedApproval' WHEN (req.FROM_DATE IS NULL AND ta.DATE_ IS null) THEN 'DontNeedApproval' ELSE 'Incomplete' END) AS approval, (CASE WHEN req.INPUTTYPE=0 THEN 'Web_Attendance' WHEN req.INPUTTYPE=1 THEN 'Request_Attendance' WHEN req.INPUTTYPE=2 THEN 'Android_Attendance' WHEN ta.date_ IS NOT NULL THEN 'Fingerprint_Attendance' ELSE 'Absent' END) AS input_type, req.LONGITUDE AS longitude, req.LATITUDE latitude FROM ALL_EMP_DAYS empDays LEFT join TIME_ATTEND ta ON ta.EMP_CODE=empDays.EMPCODE AND ta.DATE_=EMPDAYS.DD LEFT join LOGIN_USERS_REQUESTS req ON req.EMPCODE=empDays.EMPCODE AND ((req.REQUEST_TYPE=10 OR req.REQUEST_TYPE=11) and TO_DATE(req.FROM_DATE,'DD-MM-YYYY')=TO_DATE(EMPDAYS.DD,'DD-MM-YYYY') AND req.POSTED != 1 ) JOIN COMMON_EMPLOYEE emp ON emp.EMPCODE = empDays.EMPCODE ORDER BY empdays.DD,ta.time_,req.PERIOD_FROM asc;
